      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecd7",
      "text": "2026-04-25謎解き",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecd8",
      "text": ">[Cheetah_math https://x.com/Cheetah_math/status/1948654463633555928] #ちーたー謎",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecd9",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/GwsCGxTbgAI3A5D?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecda",
      "text": "\t特定できるか？[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecdb",
      "text": "\t [~ 答え側を先に思いついて逆算で解けた][caki.icon][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecdc",
      "text": "\t かなりわからなかったけど、[~ 下の問題文の枠の文字数からピンときて逆算できた][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecdd",
      "text": "\t これがわからないでいる[terang.icon][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecde",
      "text": "\t  [~ 四字熟語]になっている[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ecdf",
      "text": "\t  \t[~ カタカナかと思ってた][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ece0",
      "text": "\t  \t\t　[~ 無理難題？罵詈雑言？ 同じ文字の繰り返しにならないな〜〜]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ece1",
      "text": "\t  \t[~ 下のスラッシュで区切られているところに四字熟語のよみがあてはまるようになっている][caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ece2",
      "text": "\t  理解にいたった！ヒント[/icons/感謝.icon][terang.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00b8840000000000b2ece3",
      "text": "　　　あー[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778432133,
      "updated": 1778432133
    },
